4. Data
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  No raw or preprocessed patient data is included in this repository. Each dataset
  is used under its own data-use terms.
  - VitalDB (https://vitaldb.net/) — open surgical biosignal database.
    Lee & Jung (2018), Scientific Data 5, 180077.
  - MIMIC-III — Johnson et al. (2016), Scientific Data 3, 160035
    (credentialed access via PhysioNet).
  - eICU Collaborative Research Database, Demo 2.0.1 — Pollard et al. (2018),
    Scientific Data 5, 180178 (PhysioNet).
